title: 4 Bedroom Newly Remodeled House for rent
posting_body: ['A fully remodeled 4-bedroom and 2.5-bathroom single-family house is located in a quiet neighborhood.', 'The house has an open floorplan with ample space for entertaining and plenty of natural light.', 'The windows and sliding doors are newly installed and are energy efficient.', 'The house is less than 4 miles from The Domain and the new Apple campus.', 'Kitchen: Completely remodeled with new countertops and cabinets.', 'All brand-new appliances that have never been used.', 'The open floor plan provides easy access to the dining area, back patio, and living room.', 'Master bedroom and bathroom: The master bedroom located at the back of the house has lots of privacy and has an attached master bathroom and closet.', 'The master bathroom is fully updated with his/her sinks and a spa-like walk-in shower Guest Bedrooms and bathroom:', 'The three guest bedrooms provide ample space for kids, extended families, or for work-from-home office spaces/workout rooms.', 'Each bedroom has plenty of closet space.', 'The guest bathroom is fully remodeled with his/her sinks and an updated bathtub.', 'There is plenty of space in the bathroom for linen storage.', 'Study/Office: Study/Office space with a French door is in the front of the house and is large and spacious for any work-from-home individuals.', 'Covered back patio: The covered back patio provides great space for entertainment.', 'The sliding doors provide easy access to the dining area and the kitchen from the back patio.', 'Garage:', 'The garage can accommodate 2 cars and can be used as storage.', 'Storage Shed:', 'The backyard has a large covered storage shed that can be used for storing items like bikes, tools, holiday decorations, etc., or can be used as a workshop.', 'Laundry and Half bath: A brand new washer and dryer are installed at the back of the house next to a half bath.']
